arget":"recfrXyxhuYOczKTm","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recfhXfeeT8pTaEQB","target":"recQoK9KFveLh556S","label":"event"},{"source":"recfhXfeeT8pTaEQB","target":"recIu7xhASS4Ufyfd","label":"event"},{"source":"recfhXfeeT8pTaEQB","target":"recVrh6Nbm3PruADf","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"recEh9GSGWMBvaTAe","ref":"Acts.2.1","text":"And when the day of Pentecost was fully come, they were all with one accord in one place.","year":33},{"id":"recYH2CnVgCS48fAv","ref":"Acts.2.2","text":"And suddenly there came a sound from heaven as of a rushing mighty wind, and it filled all the house where they were sitting.","year":33},{"id":"recZD1WyQs7lRLwCB","ref":"Acts.2.3","text":"And there appeared unto them cloven tongues like as of fire, and it sat upon each of them.","year":33},{"id":"recHeN9TPsxsR099Q","ref":"Acts.2.4","text":"And they were all filled with the Holy Ghost, and began to speak with other tongues, as the Spirit gave them utterance.","year":33},{"id":"rec3xEgV17D57Ty1M","ref":"Acts.2.5","text":"And there were dwelling at Jerusalem Jews, devout men, out of every nation under heaven.","year":33},{"id":"recdnRlCTJ1LgPk65","ref":"Acts.2.6","text":"Now when this was noised abroad, the multitude came together, and were confounded, because that every man heard them speak in his own language.","year":33},{"id":"rectlCLO8MglcU7JT","ref":"Acts.2.7","text":"And they were all amazed and marvelled, saying one to another, Behold, are not all these which speak Galilaeans?","year":33},{"id":"recwK9b96HsqDQxWM","ref":"Acts.2.8","text":"And how hear we every man in our own tongue, wherein we were born?","year":33}]}
